Package se.arkalix.dto

Interface DtoWritable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    JsonCollection, JsonValue, JsonWritable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonArray, JsonBoolean, JsonNull, JsonNumber, JsonObject, JsonString
    public interface DtoWritable
    Represents a type that can be represented as any out of some non-empty set of encodings.

    Do not implement this interface directly. It is implemented automatically by generated DTO classes. Even though the interface specifies no methods, it being implemented by a class signals that the class satisfies certain requirements always fulfilled by the mentioned type of generated DTO classes.
